  "body": "### Describe the feature\n\nIt should be possible to do this:\r\n\r\n```\r\nexpect(await myContract.operator()).to.equal(operator);\r\n```\r\ninstead of this:\r\n```\r\nexpect(await myContract.operator()).to.equal(await operator.getAddress());\r\n```\r\n\r\nNot sure if it's possible because `getAddress` is async :disappointed: \r\n\r\nOne option would be to have a different matcher? `.to.be.addressable(signer);`?\n\n### Search terms\n\nsigner address addressable matchers",
